%% Paste at mermaid dot live to export a picture for the report

flowchart TD
  E[Device event from telemetry and network]
  S[Model gives anomaly score zero to one]
  B{Risk bucket from your policy}
  T[Analyst checks context]
  A[Act. patch isolate or watch]
  V[Final call on the case]

  E --> S
  S --> B
  B -->|low| M[Routine watch]
  B -->|mid| T
  B -->|high| A
  T --> V
  A --> V
  M --> V

  style B fill:#f4d35e,stroke:#333
  style S fill:#2E86AB,color:#fff
  style V fill:#6B8E23,color:#fff
